                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7031" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1099</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9202 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">看门人失守：五洋债赔偿案下审计责任的思考</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The failure of the gatekeeper: Thinking about the audit responsibility under the Compensation case of Wuyang Debt(macro case)</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙思惟，蔡世霖，侯媛敏，陈艺涛，李嘉钦，林丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">五洋建设集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">5 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">审计责任；合理保证；勤勉尽责；五洋债；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Audit responsibility; Reasonable guarantee; Diligence and responsibility; Wuyang Debt；Micro case</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015年7月，五洋建设以虚假财务信息骗取15五洋债、15五洋02债券的发行资格。2020年12月31日，杭州市中级人民法院对“五洋债”案做出一审判决：大信会计在未获取充分、适当的审计证据加以验证的前提下，认可五洋建设关于应收账款和应付账款对抵的账务处理，大信会计作为审计机构出具存在虚假记载的审计报告，未勤勉尽职，存在重大过错，需承担7.41亿连带赔偿责任。案件判决后立刻引起了公众对于审计责任大小问题的争论。本案例将将“五洋债”案件中的关键争论点逐条呈现，引导学生通过分析该案件的争论焦点，进而掌握审计责任方面的相关知识。通过该案例的学习来帮助学生更加深入地去思考如何既保障资本市场投资者的合法权益，又能为注册会计师行业的健康成长提供空间的问题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In July 2015, Wuyang Construction defrauded the issuing qualification of 15 Wuyang bonds and 15 Wuyang 02 bonds by false financial information. On December 31, 2020, Hangzhou Intermediate People&#39;s Court made a judgment of the first instance on the case of &quot;Wuyang Debt&quot; : Accounting in big letter did not obtain sufficient and appropriate audit evidence verified under the premise of recognition penta-ocean construction about accounts receivable and accounts payable on arrival of the accounting treatment, accounting as the audit institutions in the big letter false audit reports, not due diligence, diligence, major fault bear 741 million joint and several liability to pay compensation. After the judgment of the case, the public immediately caused a debate on the size of the audit responsibility. This case will present the key arguments in the case of &quot;Wuyang Debt&quot; one by one, and guide students to master the relevant knowledge of audit responsibility by analyzing the arguments in the case. Through the study of this case to help students to think more deeply about how to not only protect the legitimate rights and interests of investors in the capital market, but also provide space for the healthy growth of the CPA industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《审计学》、《审计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">审计责任、会计责任的定义和分类；审计责任中的勤勉尽责、合理保证的定义和内容；审计风险模型、审计风险和审计责任的关系；审计需求的三大理论和“深口袋”理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-01</td>
                            </tr>
